      "author": "RanceLee233",
      "description": "## Mini Calendar 0.3.4\n\n### 新增 / New\n\n- 新增可选「高亮今天的星期 / Highlight today's weekday」设置，默认关闭。开启后表头会将今天对应的星期文字标红，并在文字上方显示一个 4px 红色圆点，方便快速定位当日。\n- Optional setting to color today's weekday label red and show a 4px red dot above it in the header row. Disabled by default.\n\n### 安装 / Install\n\n下载 `main.js`、`manifest.json`、`styles.css` 放入 `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/mini-calendar/`，重启 Obsidian 后启用。\n\nDownload `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/mini-calendar/`, then enable the plugin in Obsidian.",
