      "description": "## What's new\n\n- Add Chinese and English interface text.\n- Add locale, Monday, and Sunday week-start options.\n- Add an optional ISO week number.\n- Confirm only when creating missing notes for past or future dates; today and existing notes never prompt.\n- Show a clear notice when the Daily Notes core plugin is disabled.\n- Add Chinese and English screenshots to the README.\n- Fix weekend rounding when Sunday is the first day of the week.",
