      "author": "RanceLee233",
      "description": "Initial release.\n\n- Embed a compact one-week calendar below Obsidian's built-in file explorer.\n- Open or create Daily Notes using the core plugin's folder, filename format, and template.\n- Show indicators for existing notes and unfinished tasks.\n- Support light and dark themes, desktop, and mobile.\n\nInspired by Notebook Navigator's compact calendar presentation. Thank you to Johan Sanneblad.",
